    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK654">
<l>iṭukkaṇ variṉu miḷivanta ceyyār </l>
<l>naṭukkaṟṟa kāṭci yavar</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who have infallible judgement though threatened with peril will not do acts which have brought disgrace (on former ministers).</l>
